Kanchenjunga Trekking Tour in Sikkim Himalayas ( India ) ...The Goechala Trek with Clutural Tours included.


This is undoubtedly the most popular Trek ~ Tour in Sikkim & Darjeeling area and framed for superb mountain views, a floral spectacle in summer, birds and views of pristine forests. The trek passes through the Kanchendzonga Bio-Sphere Reserve Forests and special trekking permits with fees are paid. This package gives complete travels in the mountains with visits to MONASTERIES and also is able to meet the local people and understand their lifestyles. It’s different-Be assured.
